quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  56,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  56,1,jab woh honay wala waqea paish aa jaye ga
  56,2,to koi is ke wuqoo ko jhutlanay wala nah hoga
  56,3,woh teh o baala kar dainay wali aafat hogi
  56,4,zameen is waqt yaqbargi hila daali jaye gi
  56,5,aur pahar is terhan rezah rezah kar diye jayen ge
  56,6,ke paragandah gubhar ban kar reh jayen ge
  56,7,tum log uss waqt teen garohoon mein taqseem ho jao ge
  56,8,"dayen baazu walay, so dayen baazu walon ( ki khush naseebi ) ka kya kehna"
  56,9,"aur baen baazu walay, to baen baazu walon ( ki bad naseebi ka ) ka kya thikana"
  56,10,aur agay walay to phir agay wa le hi hain
  56,11,wohi to Maqarrab log hain
  56,12,Nemat bharijannaton mein rahen ge
  56,13,uglo mein se bohat hon ge
  56,14,aur pichlon mein se kam
  56,15,murassa takhton par
  56,16,takiye laga ye aamnay samnay bathain ge
  56,17,unn ki mjlson mein abdi larke sharaab chashma jari se
  56,18,labraiz pyaale kntr aur saghar liye dorrtay phirtay hunge
  56,19,jisay pi kar nah unn ka sir chukra-ay ga nah un ki aqal mein futoor aeye ga
  56,20,aur woh unn ke samnay terhan terhan ke lazeez phal paish karen ge jisay chahain chunn len
  56,21,aur parindon ke gosht paish karen ge ke jis parinday ka chahain istemaal karen
  56,22,aur un ke liye khobsorat aankhon wali hooren hongi
  56,23,aisi Hussain jaisay chhupa kar rakhay hue moti
  56,24,yeh sab kuch unn aamaal ki jaza ke tor par inhen miley ga jo woh duniya mein karte rahay thay
  56,25,wahan woh koi behooda kalaam ya gunah ki baat nah sunen ge
  56,26,jo baat bhi hogi theek theek hogi
  56,27,"aur dayen baazu walay, dayen baazu walon ki khush naseebi ka kya kehna"
  56,28,woh be- khaar baryon(babhair kantay ki bari)
  56,29,aur teh Bar teh charrhey hue kalon
  56,30,aur daur taq phaily hui chaon
  56,31,aur har dam rawan pani
  56,32,aur kabhi khatam nah honay walay
  56,33,aur be rok toak milnay walay bakasrat phalon
  56,34,aur onche nashist gaahon mein hon ge
  56,35,un ki biwion ko hum khaas tor par naye suray se peda karen ge
  56,36,aur inhen ba kurrah bana den ge
  56,37,apne shoharon ki aashiq aur Umar mein hum sun
  56,38,yeh kuch dayen baazu walon ke liye hai
  56,39,woh uglo mein se bohat hon ge
  56,40,aur pichlon mein se bhi bohat
  56,41,"aur baen baazu walay, baen baazu walon ki bad naseebi ka kya poochna"
  56,42,woh lau ki lapat aur kholtey hue pani
  56,43,aur kalay dhowen ke saaye mein hon ge
  56,44,jo nah thanda hoga nah aaraam da
  56,45,yeh woh log hon ge jo iss injaam ko pounchanay se pehlay khushaal thay
  56,46,aur gunah azeem par israar karte thay
  56,47,"kehte thay"" kya jab hum mar kar khaak ho jayen ge aur hadion ka panjar reh jayen ge to phir utha kharray kiye jayen ge ?"
  56,48,"aur kya hamaray woh baap dada bhi uthaye jayen ge jo pehlay guzar chuke hain? """
  56,49,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn logon se kaho, yaqeenan aglay aur pichlle sab"
  56,50,aik din zaroor jama kiye jaane walay hain jis ka waqt muqarrar kya ja chuka hai
  56,51,phir ae gumraho aur jhutlanay walo !
  56,52,tum shajar zarqoom ki ghiza khanay walay ho
  56,53,usi se tum pait bharo ge
  56,54,aur oopar se kholta howa pani
  56,55,tons lagey hue oont ki terhan piyo ge
  56,56,yeh hai baen walon ki ziyafat ka samaan roz jaza mein
  56,57,hum ne tumhe peda kya hai phir kyun tasdeeq nahi karte ?
  56,58,"kabhi tum ne ghhor kya, yeh nutfa jo tum daaltay ho"
  56,59,is se bacha tum banatay ho ya is ke bananay walay hum hain ?
  56,60,"hum ne tumahray darmain mout ko taqseem kya hai, aur hum iss se aajiz nahi hain"
  56,61,ke tumhari shakalain badal den aur kisi aisi shakal mein tumhe peda kar den jis ko tum nahi jantay
  56,62,"apni pehli paidaiesh ko to tum jantay ho, phir kyun sabaq nahi letay ?"
  56,63,"kabhi tum ne socha, yeh beej jo tum botay ho"
  56,64,inn se khityan tum ogatay ho ya unn ke ugane walay hum hain ?
  56,65,hum chahain to un kheetion ko bhus bana kar rakh den aur tum terhan terhan ki baatein banatay reh jao
  56,66,ke hum par to ulti chti par gayi
  56,67,balkay hamaray to naseeb hi phootay hue hain
  56,68,"kabhi tum ne ankhen khol kar dekha, yeh pani jo tum peetay ho"
  56,69,isay tum ne baadal se barsaya hai ya iss ke barsane walay hum hain ?
  56,70,"hum chahain to usay sakht khaari bana kar rakh den, phir kyun tum shukar guzaar nahi hotay ?"
  56,71,"kabhi tum ne khayaal kya, yeh aag jo tum sulgatay ho"
  56,72,"iss ka darakht tum ne peda kya hai, ya is ke peda karne walay hum hain ?"
  56,73,hum ne uss ko yaad dehani ka zareya aur haajat mandoon ke liye samaan zeist banaya hai
  56,74,"pas ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, apne rab azeem ke naam ki tasbeeh karo"
  56,75,"pas nahi, mein qasam khata hon taron ke mawaqay ki"
  56,76,aur agar tum samjhoo to yeh bohat barri qasam hai
  56,77,ke yeh aik buland paya quran hai
  56,78,aik mehfooz kitaab mein Sabt
  56,79,jisay mutahareen ke siwa koi chhoo nahi sakta
  56,80,yeh rab alaalmin ka nazil kardah hai
  56,81,phir kya is kalaam ke sath tum be aitnai brtte ho
  56,82,aur iss Nemat mein apna hissa tum ne yeh rakha hai ke isay jutlatay ho ?
  56,83,to jab marnay walay ki jaan halaq taq poanch chuki hoti hai
  56,84,"aur tum aankhon se dekh rahay hotay ho ke woh mar raha hai ,"
  56,85,uss waqt tumhari bah nisbat hum uss ke ziyada qareeb hotay hain magar tum ko nazar nahi atay
  56,86,"ab agar tum kisi ke mehkoom nahi ho aur apne iss khayaal mein sachey ho ,"
  56,87,uss waqt uss ki nikalti hui jaan ko wapas kyun nahi le atay ?
  56,88,phir woh marnay wala agar muqarabainmein se ho
  56,89,to is ke liye raahat aur umdah rizaq aur Nemat bhari jannat hai
  56,90,aur agar woh ashaab Yamin mein se ho
  56,91,"to is ka istaqbaal yun hota hai ke salam hai tujhe, to ashaab ul yameenmein se hai"
  56,92,aur agar woh jhutlanay walay gumraah logon mein se ho
  56,93,to is ki tawaza ke liye kholta howa pani hai
  56,94,aur jahannum mein jhaunka jana
  56,95,yeh sab kuch qatee haq hai
  56,96,"pas ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, apne rab azeem ke naam ki tasbeeh karo"
